      "description": "Presenting a collector-grade E46 M3 in pristine condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, paired with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanical integrity is paramount: the VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced. The vehicle maintains factory-spec compression across all cylinders and a leak-free profile. Suspension geometry remains precise with fresh bushings and Bilstein dampers, while the limited-slip differential provides optimal torque distribution. Finished in immaculate paint with an interior devoid of bolster fatigue, this is a mechanically sorted, turn-key investment for the serious driver.",
