      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty. I\u2019ve babied this car since the day I got it, and it honestly looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It\u2019s in incredible shape\u2014sparkling clean inside and out, with that 'new car' feel still going strong. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to have a blast behind the wheel. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and kept in pristine condition, this is the one for you. Come say hi and take it for a spin!",
